flowchart LR
    A[Start] --> B{Dependencies OK?}

    B -->|No| C[Exit]
    B -->|Yes| D{Git Clean?}

    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E[Checkout Main]

    E --> F[Pull Latest]
    F --> G[Create Branch]

    G --> H[Run AI Loop]

    H --> I{.stuck exists?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Print Error]
    J --> K[Exit Failed]

    I -->|No| L{.complete exists?}

    L -->|Yes| M[Stop Loop]
    L -->|No| N{Iterations Left?}

    N -->|Yes| H
    N -->|No| M

    M --> O[Push Branch]

    O --> P[Review Changes]

    P --> Q[Done]
